{"tid":2186561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美將截斷中共和伊朗間軍火交易","createTime":"2020-09-03T04:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T05:38:59.000Z","uid":169081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63c01a0c9742c5f964b435c03fb2b375d4b3174c","tid":2186561,"uid":169081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"2020年10月28日，因為聯合國對伊朗的伊朗武器禁運條例，將在這天「過期」 。武器禁運條例失效，意味著伊朗將具備出口武器設備給他國，以及引進先進武器的資格。<br />\n<br />\n8月31日蓬佩奧接受了WMAL-FM電台的採訪，被問到伊朗與中共正在考慮建立25年的戰略夥伴關係，這將如何改變世界的格局？<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧回答，中共在伊朗有一些重要利益，「世界上兩個最嚴重的基本人權侵犯者臭味相投，這個一點都不奇怪。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-09-02/65844882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-09-02%2F65844882&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=76390f02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-09-02/65844882</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=vf4JLF4lz6Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvf4JLF4lz6Y&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=1405cc81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=vf4JLF4lz6Y</a>"},{"pid":"13ee3056215dc8568d816eb8d8b4f5374766f7a4","tid":2186561,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"聯合國廢左  好采世界仲有美國堅持住"},{"pid":"bfe2c3e86b85a528bf978679a1c90df2069e37bb","tid":2186561,"uid":276548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"美國上緊火<br />\n咩伊朗 北韓而家都收晒皮<br />\n唔敢玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdce2cf2a8ae0723e2c3e517f696ac92f13041c4","tid":2186561,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal